%N A156301 a(n) = ceiling( n * log_3(2) ) = ceiling(n * 0.6309297535714574371...).
%C A156301 a(n) is the unique k such that 1/2 <= 3^a(n)/2^(n+1) < 3/2. Equality occurs iff n = 0. See Gorman-Huang and Marks.
